{"tid":1075560,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋世寶自由身賺多咗","createTime":"2019-03-24T08:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T01:47:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"90de04b9f22b6c68c3113900f6c1bc8ab54a9799","tid":1075560,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:42:00.000Z","msg":"人蓋世寶昨午為ViuTV兒童節目《快樂童盟》錄影，她表示未離開無綫時，ViuTV已開始接觸她傾合作：「當時我覺得要尊重舊公司同合約精神，今次都係做嘉賓啫。」離開無綫約一個月，她直言收多了邀她工作的電話：「都有經理人公司接觸，但我唔想咁快有束縛，依家真係好自由。（多咗兒童產品代言？）有，但美容產品工作仲多，我仲乘機去V面同打眼袋槍，以前我好懶保養，依家要勤力啲嘞！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_gbuZLGsvs3ecv6dpEougg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/11d95841f404a0065301acd9ce120ff6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_gbuZLGsvs3ecv6dpEougg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F11d95841f404a0065301acd9ce120ff6&h=5a511934&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aafa3da268503b801df20a943eb35adde08304c2","tid":1075560,"uid":62822,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29b5b76a75648247637a13afd366f3346ce6b4db","tid":1075560,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9004f05f4e7b581806711a8a833b27e8c64da21d","tid":1075560,"uid":153305,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"who fucking care?"},{"pid":"eda5feb20083cacf40ca5d8f3f87325cb1baa419","tid":1075560,"uid":182846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3973f2f47093ae23167a4d425a23000cb883049","tid":1075560,"uid":50176,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0